Susie Garrett https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Susie_Garrett 0 Susie Garrett (December 29, 1929 – May 24, 2002) was an African American actress of theatre and television, jazz vocalist, and acting teacher. She is best known for playing Betty Johnson on the TV series Punky Brewster.
